        "bn2-bg gradient <-> canvas gradient-line (source-guarded)"
      ],
      "risks": [
        { "ctrl": "_bn2Lines.read/write", "level": "med", "line": 14, "why": "Entire lines UI depends on window._bn2Lines (read/write/normalize). If that global is undefined, line read returns [] (line 14 guarded) so panel renders zero rows, but line-add handler (line 277) calls window._bn2Lines.write/normalize UNGUARDED → throws on click. Hard dependency on external global with no fallback for mutators." },
        { "ctrl": "bn2-w/bn2-h", "level": "low", "line": 184, "why": "No min/max clamp in JS (only HTML attr). User can type out-of-range; HTML min/max not enforced on programmatic 'change'. Cosmetic." }
      ]
    },
